  %p If you are a developer you can contribute with some of the features or check our code repository
  %div
    = link_to _('Visit our backlog'), RememberMe::Application.config.backlog_url, :class => "button fbulb left"
    = link_to _('Check the source code'), RememberMe::Application.config.source_code_url, :class => "button fimport left"
    .clear
.clear
